title: Knock 'em Dead 2014 The Ultimate Job Search Guide by Martin Yate
description:
The definitive guide for job search success in today's volatile market!

For more than twenty-five years, author Martin Yate has shown the way for millions of job seekers. In this new edition of his New York Times bestselling series, Yate helps you build a killer resume, maximize your social networks to find more job opportunities, and understand what employers are really looking for in the people they hire. He'll also show you how to turn job interviews into job offers with advice on how to stand out from the competition.

With millions of Americans competing in a limited employment pool, there's no better way to career success than by using Martin Yate's unique, proven, and time-tested methods to land the job you want and move ahead in your professional career.
